OL,5,G2100 Ambulance: Code Red
OL,6,     FA man suffers repeated cardiac
OL,7,     Farrests as medics fight to save
OL,8,     Fhim, while paramedics rush to
OL,9,     Ftreat another man severely burned
OL,10,     Fby a gas canister explosion on a
