OL,5,G2300 He Kills Coppers
OL,6,     FThree policemen are murdered
OL,7,     Fduring the 1966 World Cup
OL,8,     Fcelebrations, and three men are
OL,9,     Fconnected to the deaths: policeman
OL,10,     FFrank; journalist and witness
OL,11,     FTony; and Billy - the murderer.
OL,12,     F(Ep1/3)
OL,13,G0005 He Kills Coppers
OL,14,     FBilly goes on the run, while
OL,15,     Freporter Tony is in demand as the
OL,16,     Facknowledged expert on the cop
OL,17,     Fkiller. But five years on, Frank's
OL,18,     Flife is blighted by his failure to
OL,19,     Fcapture the villain. (Ep2/3)
